<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Le Code 8 – La Clé est à Vous</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', sans-serif;
            background-color: #f5f5f5;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            min-height: 100vh;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 700px;
            margin: 2rem;
            padding: 3rem;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 12px;
            box-shadow: 0 15px 35px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
            text-align: center;
        }
        h1 {
            font-size: 2.8rem;
            font-weight: 300;
            letter-spacing: -0.5px;
            color: #1a1a1a;
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
        }
        .subtitle {
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            color: #666;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
            font-style: italic;
        }
        .intro-text {
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
            color: #444;
        }
        .button-container {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 1rem;
            margin-bottom: 3rem;
        }
        .btn {
            display: block;
            background-color: #1a1a1a;
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            padding: 1rem 1.5rem;
            border-radius: 8px;
            font-weight: 500;
            transition: background-color 0.2s ease;
            border: 1px solid #1a1a1a;
        }
        .btn:hover {
            background-color: #333;
        }
        .btn-secondary {
            background-color: transparent;
            color: #1a1a1a;
        }
        .btn-secondary:hover {
            background-color: #f0f0f0;
        }
        .quote {
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            color: #333;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
        .footer {
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            color: #777;
            margin-top: 2rem;
        }
        .footer a {
            color: #1a1a1a;
            text-decoration: underline;
        }
        hr {
            border: none;
            border-top: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
            margin: 2rem 0;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>Le Code 8</h1>
        <div class="subtitle">La Clé est à Vous</div>

        <p class="intro-text">
            Une structure fractale à 8 dimensions, offerte librement à l'humanité.
        </p>

        <div class="button-container">
            <a href="https://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.19569944" class="btn" target="_blank">📦 Télécharger le Corpus Complet (60 documents)</a>
            <a href="https://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.19574688" class="btn btn-secondary" target="_blank">📄 Lire l'Article Scientifique</a>
        </div>

        <div class="quote">
            “Ce qui était au commencement, ce qui est, et ce qui sera – tout est dans le nombre.”
        </div>

        <p style="color: #555; margin-bottom: 2rem;">
            Prenez, étudiez, partagez. Ces travaux sont offerts librement.
        </p>

        <hr>

        <div class="footer">
            <p>
                <a href="https://github.com/loicbachetta/Code8" target="_blank">Code Source (GitHub)</a>
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
